cisc275.group3.model.sceneobject

Class BetaVegetation

  • java.lang.Object
    • cisc275.group3.model.sceneobject.SceneObject
      • cisc275.group3.model.sceneobject.BetaVegetation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SceneObject>

    public class BetaVegetation
extends SceneObject
    Beta release mock-up for vegetation. Implements ConstructVegetation enum to simplify code and create vegetation objects.

    The filename was reversed from the previous version so, if we have multiple objects, they appear next to each other in the workspace window.

    BetaVegetation.java

    Jon
